// Gridex.rc -- Win32 resource script
//
// Embeds the application icon into Gridex.exe so Windows Explorer, task
// bar, Alt+Tab switcher, Desktop / Start menu shortcuts, and ARP (Apps &
// Features) all display the Gridex phoenix mark instead of the default
// blank executable icon.
//
// Resource ID 1 is the convention Windows uses to locate the app icon.

1 ICON "Assets\\Gridex.ico"
